 introduction of the heterogeneity parameter exacerbates the problem.
 The likelihood function has ridges following approximately 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau\propto\sqrt{|\theta|}$
\end_inset

.
 Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "fig:contour lines"
